Kate Magowan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kate_Magowan 0 Katie Victoria "Kate" Magowan (born 1 June 1975) is an English actress. She has been in film, theatre, television and radio productions. Her best known role is Princess Una in the feature film Stardust. She is married to actor John Simm. Katie_Victoria_"_Kate_"_Magowan ( born 1_June_1975 ) is an_English_actress .
